🗝️ 📚
🧩 decode_shift(s) 👉
   length ⬅️ 📐 s
   result ⬅️ []
   i ⬅️ 0
   🌀 length 👉
      char ⬅️ s[i]
      offset ⬅️ 差(差(char, 97), 5)
      decoded_offset ⬅️ offset
      ❓ offset 📈 0 👉
         decoded_offset ⬅️ 和(offset, 26)
      🔚
      remainder ⬅️ 剰余(decoded_offset, 26)
      decoded_char ⬅️ 和(97, remainder)
      result 🧲 decoded_char
      i ⬆️
   🔚
   ✅ result
🔚
>>> decode_shift([102, 115, 105, 105, 116]) 
[97, 110, 100, 100, 111]